ence/functions/get_stage_location\nSnowflake Documentation - Directory Tables: https://docs.snowflake.com/en/sql-reference/external-tablesdirectory-tables\nSnowflake Documentation - Stages: https://docs.snowflake.com/en/user-guide/data-load-stages"
