                "question": "Which command can be used to delete staged files from a Snowflake stage when the files are no longer needed?\n",
                "choices": {
                  "A": "DELETE",
                  "B": "DROP",
                  "C": "REMOVE",
                  "D": "TRUNCATE TABLE"
