https://parquet.apache.org/ (Official Apache Parquet website with in-depth information\nabout the format).\nUnderstanding Columnar Storage: Explore resources on columnar data stores to further understand the\nbenefits of Parquet. Search specifically for \"columnar storage benefits\" for more information on how this\nconcept is applied in data warehousing and analysis."
