ch for maximizing Snowflake's data loading performance. This facilitates parallelism, optimizes\nresource utilization, and minimizes overhead, leading to faster and more reliable data ingestion.\nRefer to Snowflake documentation for more details on data loading best practices:\nSnowflake Data Loading Best Practices"
