cumentation - COPY INTO command: https://docs.snowflake.com/en/sqlreference/sql/copy-into-table.html (Pay close attention to sections regarding file tracking and\nhandling of existing files on a stage)\n2. Snowflake Blog on Data Loading: Snowflake frequently publishes blog posts and articles. Search on\nthe snowflake blog for keywords related to \"data loading\" and \"COPY INTO\" to find helpful guides.\n3. Snowflake Community Forums: https://community.snowflake.com/This should offer more insights\nand use cases."
