ntation on Data Types: https://docs.snowflake.com/en/sql-reference/datatypes.html\nSnowflake Documentation on VARIANT Data Type: https://docs.snowflake.com/en/sqlreference/data-types-semistructured.html#variant\nSnowflake Documentation on ARRAY Data Type: https://docs.snowflake.com/en/sqlreference/data-types-semistructured.html#array"
