                "question": "Which Snowflake data governance feature supports the tracking of sensitive data for compliance, discovery,\nprotection, and resource usage?\n",
                "choices": {
                  "A": "Row access policies",
                  "B": "Data classification",
                  "C": "Object dependencies",
                  "D": "Object tagging"
