                "question": "Which command removes a role from another role or a user in Snowflake?\n",
                "choices": {
                  "A": "ALTER ROLE",
                  "B": "REVOKE ROLE",
                  "C": "USE ROLE",
                  "D": "USE SECONDARY ROLES"
