rics\nSnowflake Documentation on SHOW TABLES command: https://docs.snowflake.com/en/sqlreference/sql/show-tables\nSnowflake Documentation on Information Schema TABLES view:\nhttps://docs.snowflake.com/en/sql-reference/info-schema/tables"
