                "id": 195,
                "question": "A Snowflake Administrator needs to ensure that sensitive corporate data in Snowflake tables is not visible to end\nusers, but is partially visible to functional managers.\nHow can this requirement be met?\n",
                "choices": {
                  "A": "Use data encryption.",
                  "B": "Use dynamic data masking.",
                  "C": "Use secure materialized views.",
                  "D": "Revoke all roles for functional managers and end users."
