              {
                "id": 405,
                "question": "A developer is granted ownership of a table that has a masking policy. The developer’s role is not able to see the\nmasked data.\nWill the developer be able to modify the table to read the masked data?\n",
                "choices": {
                  "A": "Yes, because a table owner has full control and can unset masking policies.",
                  "B": "Yes, because masking policies only apply to cloned tables.",
