ke.com/en/sql-reference/sql/alteraccount.html#parameters (This link directly to the documentation section about activating network policies).\nSnowflake Documentation on CREATE NETWORK POLICY: https://docs.snowflake.com/en/sqlreference/sql/create-network-policy.html (Detailed information on creating network policies).\nSnowflake Documentation on Network Policy: https://docs.snowflake.com/en/sql-reference/ddl-networkpolicy.html (Overview of network policies)."
