rough ALTER ACCOUNT commands, with administrative privileges not limited solely to the\nORGADMIN role.\nAuthoritative Links:\nSnowflake Documentation on Network Policies: https://docs.snowflake.com/en/sql-reference/sql/createnetwork-policy\nSnowflake Documentation on Network Policy Management: https://docs.snowflake.com/en/sqlreference/sql/alter-account"
