es: This page lists and defines all the\nprivileges in Snowflake, including OWNERSHIP, USAGE, MODIFY and CREATE.\nSnowflake Documentation on Database Roles: This documentation outlines roles, which are used\nto manage permissions and which determine access control to various database objects."
