rmation, refer to:\nSnowflake Documentation on Architecture: https://docs.snowflake.com/en/user-guide/intro-keyconcepts.html#snowflake-architecture\nCloud Computing Concepts: https://aws.amazon.com/what-is-cloud-computing/"
