lated to Snowflake's\narchitecture and features.\n3. Cloud Data Platform Concepts: Resources that discuss the concepts of shared-nothing, shared-disk,\nand cloud-native architectures, such as vendor-specific cloud documentation for S3, Azure Blob\nStorage, and Google Cloud Storage."
