egion benefits. Option D limits accounts to the same region even when deployed in different\nclouds.\nAuthoritative Link:\nSnowflake Documentation: This documentation provides an overview of Snowflake's architecture, features,\nand capabilities.\nWhile a specific page directly stating this fact is hard to pin down due to the breadth of Snowflake's\ndocumentation, understanding the multi-cloud deployment model throughout the documentation implies this\nflexibility. Look for sections on regions, cloud provider support, and disaster recovery in the Snowflake\ndocumentation. (https://docs.snowflake.com/)"
