                "question": "Which of the following is an example of an operation that can be completed without requiring compute, assuming\nno queries have been executed previously?\n",
                "choices": {
                  "A": "SELECT SUM (ORDER_AMT) FROM SALES;",
                  "B": "SELECT AVG(ORDER_QTY) FROM SALES;",
                  "C": "SELECT MIN(ORDER_AMT) FROM SALES;",
                  "D": "SELECT ORDER_AMT * ORDER_QTY FROM SALES;"
