                "question": "If a virtual warehouse runs for 61 seconds, shuts down, and then restarts and runs for 30 seconds, for how many\nseconds is it billed?\n",
                "choices": {
                  "A": "60",
                  "B": "91",
                  "C": "120",
                  "D": "121"
                },
                "answer": [
