ons. The key takeaway is the flexibility\nand configurability offered by Snowflake's virtual warehouse architecture.\nSupporting Links:\nSnowflake SnowSQL configuration: https://docs.snowflake.com/en/user-guide/snowsql-config.html\nSnowflake Virtual Warehouse sizing: https://docs.snowflake.com/en/user-guide/warehousesconsiderations.html\nSnowflake ODBC Driver configuration: https://docs.snowflake.com/en/user-guide/odbc-parameters.html"
