default behavior without this parameter is asynchronous; Snowflake returns\nimmediately, and the resize happens in the background.\nFor authoritative information, refer to the official Snowflake documentation on ALTER WAREHOUSE:\nhttps://docs.snowflake.com/en/sql-reference/sql/alter-warehouse.html"
