neck and reducing query wait times.\nThis is the fundamental concept of horizontal scaling. Therefore, increasing MAX_CLUSTER_COUNT is the\nmost recommended action for this scenario.\nAuthoritative Links:\nSnowflake Documentation on Multi-Cluster Warehouses - This provides a detailed explanation of multicluster warehouses and how they scale.\nSnowflake Documentation on Warehouse Parameters - This lists and explains all the parameters for\nwarehouse creation including those discussed above."
