:\nBUILD_SCOPED_FILE_URL: Details on using scoped URLs.\nGET_PRESIGNED_URL: Documentation for pre-signed URLs.\nSecure Views: Understanding Secure Views and their functionality.\nUnstructured Data: Information about working with unstructured data in Snowflake."
