 on External Tables and Scoped URLs:\nhttps://docs.snowflake.com/en/sql-reference/external-tables-introduction\n2. Snowflake Documentation on Secure Data Sharing: https://docs.snowflake.com/en/userguide/data-sharing-intro\n3. AWS Documentation on Pre-signed URLs:\nhttps://docs.aws.amazon.com/AmazonS3/latest/userguide/using-presigned-urls.html"
