ke's robust SQL engine and features make it possible to combine\ndata from various sources (including Data Marketplace) directly, often without extensive transformations.\nAuthoritative Links:\nSnowflake Data Marketplace: https://www.snowflake.com/data-marketplace/\nSecure Data Sharing: https://docs.snowflake.com/en/user-guide/data-sharing-intro.html"
