g concurrency and related concepts.)\nQuery Processing: https://docs.snowflake.com/en/user-guide/querying.html (Details the query execution\nprocess and how warehouses are involved.)\nThese resources will further clarify how concurrency, warehouse sizing, and queuing mechanics interact\nwithin the Snowflake ecosystem."
