                "id": 440,
                "question": "A Snowflake user has a query that is running for a long time. When the user opens the query profiler, it indicates\nthat a lot of data is spilling to disk.\nWhat is causing this to happen?\n",
                "choices": {
                  "A": "The result cache is almost full and is unable to hold the results.",
                  "B": "The cloud storage staging area is not sufficient to hold the data results.",
