tly tied to execution time, credit consumptionis evaluated outside of the profile analysis.\nHere are some resources for more information:\nSnowflake Documentation on Query Profile: https://docs.snowflake.com/en/ui/queryprofile.html\nUnderstanding Cartesian Joins: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cartesian_product\nIn summary, Query Profile allows identification of Cartesian products (inefficient joins)\nand memory related spillages(queries exceeding available memory) through\nvisualization of query execution plan."
