he sections regarding scan and partitions)\nSnowflake Documentation on Micro-partitions: https://docs.snowflake.com/en/userguide/tables-clustering-micropartitions.html\nSnowflake Documentation on Pruning: https://docs.snowflake.com/en/sqlreference/constructs/pruning.html"
