les\nand schema.\nAuthoritative Links:\nSnowflake Time Travel: https://docs.snowflake.com/en/user-guide/data-recovery-time-travel.htmlUNDROP SCHEMA: https://docs.snowflake.com/en/sql-reference/sql/undrop-schema.html"
